Package com.telenav.kivakit.annotations.code.change

Annotation Interface TypeChange

@Retention(SOURCE) @Target(TYPE) public @interface TypeChange
Indicates a (potentially incompatible) code change to a type.

Example

 @MethodChange(change = METHOD_REMOVED,
               previously = "void myOldMethod(int value)",
               version = "1.8.0")
 class MyClass
 {
     [...]
 }
Author:
jonathanl (shibo)
